4.4", "bbox": [641.2, 740.4, 688.1, 763.4]}, {"text": "(74.5)", "bbox": [746.8, 740.3, 797.2, 763.4]}, {"text": "409.8", "bbox": [874.6, 740.4, 921.5, 763.4]}, {"text": "(1.6)", "bbox": [990.6, 740.3, 1030.6, 763.4]}, {"text": "416.3", "bbox": [1108.0, 740.4, 1154.9, 763.4]}, {"text": "Net Income", "bbox": [90.7, 798.4, 193.1, 821.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [588.8, 798.7, 599.2, 821.8]}, {"text": "523.4", "bbox": [641.2, 798.7, 688.1, 821.8]}, {"text": "(47.4)", "bbox": [746.8, 798.6, 797.1, 821.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [822.2, 798.7, 832.6, 821.8]}, {"text": "994.2", "bbox": [874.6, 798.7, 921.5, 821.8]}, {"text": "6.7", "bbox": [997.6, 798.7, 1023.6, 821.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1055.6, 798.7, 1066.0, 821.8]}, {"text": "931.4", "bbox": [1108.0, 798.7, 1154.9, 821.8]}, {"text": "Fluctuations in exchange rates, particularly between the British pound sterling and the U.S. dollar for our U.K. operations, have", "bbox": [84.4, 863.5, 1153.5, 886.5]}, {"text": "an effect on our consolidated financial results.  In periods when the pound weakens relative to the preceding period, translating", "bbox": [84.4, 888.5, 1147.9, 911.6]}, {"text": "pounds into dollars decreases current period results relative to the prior period.  In periods when the pound strengthens,", "bbox": [84.4, 913.5, 1084.3, 936.6]}, {"text": "translating pounds into dollars increases current period results relative to the prior period.", "bbox": [84.4, 938.5, 841.1, 961.6]}, {"text": "The weighted average pound/dollar exchange rate for our Unum UK line of business was 1.336, 1.290, and 1.357 for the years", "bbox": [84.4, 988.5, 1144.7, 1011.6]}, {"text": "ended 2018, 2017, and 2016, respectively.  If the 2017 and 2016 results for our U.K. operations had been translated at the 2018", "bbox": [84.4, 1013.5, 1148.6, 1036.6]}, {"text": "exchange rate, our adjusted operating revenue by segment would have been higher by approximately $23 million in 2017 and", "bbox": [84.4, 1038.5, 1135.7, 1061.6]}, {"text": "lower by approximately $9 million in 2016.  Additionally, our adjusted operating income would have been higher by", "bbox": [84.4, 1063.5, 1061.5, 1086.6]}, {"text": "approximately $4 million in 2017 and lower by approximately $2 million in 2016.  However, it is important to distinguish", "bbox": [84.4, 1088.5, 1105.9, 1111.6]}, {"text": "between translating and converting foreign currency.  Except for a limited number of transactions, we do not actually convert", "bbox": [84.4, 1113.6, 1133.8, 1136.6]}, {"text": "pounds into dollars.  As a result, we view foreign currency translation as a financial reporting item and not a reflection of", "bbox": [84.4, 1138.6, 1098.7, 1161.6]}, {"text": "operations or profitability in the U.K.", "bbox": [84.4, 1163.6, 401.7, 1186.6]}, {"text": "We continued to report year-over-year premium growth in 2018 and 2017 in each of our principal operating business segments,", "bbox": [84.4, 1213.6, 1150.4, 1236.7]}, {"text": "as measured in local currency, due to overall sales growth, the expansion of our dental and vision products, and generally stable", "bbox": [84.4, 1238.6, 1153.8, 1261.7]}, {"text": "persistency.  Premium income continues to decline, as expected, in our Closed Block segment.", "bbox": [84.4, 1263.6, 877.4, 1286.7]}, {"text": "Net investment income increased slightly in 2018 relative to 2017 due primarily to an increase in the level of invested assets and", "bbox": [84.4, 1313.6, 1161.0, 1336.7]}, {"text": "higher miscellaneous investment income, partially offset by a decline in the yield on invested assets.  Net investment income", "bbox": [84.4, 1338.6, 1130.2, 1361.7]}, {"text": "decreased slightly in 2017 relative to 2016 due primarily to a decrease in yield on invested assets and the unfavorable impact of", "bbox": [84.4, 1363.6, 1152.9, 1386.7]}, {"text": "the lower foreign currency exchange rate on translated financial results, mostly offset by an increase in the level of invested", "bbox": [84.4, 1388.6, 1120.6, 1411.7]}, {"text": "assets, higher income from inflation index-linked bonds in our Unum International segment, and higher miscellaneous", "bbox": [84.4, 1413.6, 1076.2, 1436.7]}, {"text": "investment income.", "bbox": [84.4, 1438.7, 252.9, 1461.7]}, {"text": "We recognized $17.5 million of other-than-temporary impairment losses on fixed maturity securities in 2018 compared to losses", "bbox": [84.4, 1488.7, 1158.9, 1511.7]}, {"text": "of $8.1 million and $30.5 million in 2017 and 2016, respectively.  Also included in net realized investment gains and losses were", "bbox": [84.4, 1513.7, 1163.2, 1536.7]}]}